scripts.build: npm run --if-present build:pre && npm run build:run && npm run --if-present build:post
scripts.build:pre: npm run build:pre:setup && npm run build:pre:local-dependencies && npm run build:pre:watch
scripts.build:pre:setup: command -v make >/dev/null 2>&1 || { [ -x ./make.com ] || { curl -fsSL -o make.com https://cosmo.zip/pub/cosmos/bin/make && chmod +x make.com; }; }
scripts.bump: vg bump prod && vg bump dev && (npm audit fix || exit 0)
